summary: LETTER FROM MERLE FELLING (MN) OPPOSING  THOSE PROVISIONS OF EARLY WARNING REPORT (EWR) REGULATIOS THAT REQUIRE MANUFACTURERS THAT PRODUCE OVER 500 SMALL-TO-MEDIUM TRAILERS (THOSE WITH A GROSS VEHICLE WEIGHT RATING, GVWR, OF 26000 POUNDS) TO ISSUE A COMPREHENSISIVE EARLY WARNING REPORT TO HTSA. SUCH REPORTING. ACCORDING TO SENATOR MARK DAYTON, WOULD PUT MR FELLING AND SOME OF HIS COLLEAGUES IN THE TRAILERS OUT OF BUSINESS.  *AK
